Sunday, I’ll be back in Leavenworth for the day, then pack up my booth and take everything home in my Jeep. It’ll stay in my Jeep, in the garage, until I do next week’s show in Leavenworth. Anyone who thinks making and selling art is easy should step into an artist’s shoes for a few weeks and see for themselves.
